<div class="story"><p>Harbour Bay is a relatively new subdivision in Kitty Hawk with 36 large building lots, all large enough to accommodate a spacious home with a pool. Situated on Kitty Hawk Bay, the community of Harbour Bay features open water views across Kitty Hawk Bay and distant ocean horizon views. Perfect for storm watching. Harbour Bay has an active home owners association which oversees the community pool deeded water access on Kitty Hawk Bay with a parking lot and boardwalk to the bay front and the Moor Shores Rd multi- use trail. You can find Harbour Bay nestled between the communities of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/first-flight-ridge.asp" title="First Flight Ridge">First Flight Ridge</a> to the north and <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/kitty-dunes-heights.asp" title="Kitty Dunes Heights">Kitty Dunes Heights</a> to the south. </p><p><a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/harbour-bay-covenants.pdf" title="Harbour Bay Covenants">Harbour Bay Covenants</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/harbour-bay-bylaws.pdf" title="Harbour Bay Bylaws">Harbour Bay Bylaws</a>   - - - <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/Covenant-Disclaimer.asp" target="_blank"><b>    *</b></a></p>
    
